data.description: Welcome to your canvas for creativity on Oak Creek Parkway! This charming home offers the most affordable price per square foot in this sought-after location. Step inside and experience the incredible flow pattern that makes this home a standout. The seamless transition from room to room creates a welcoming and harmonious atmosphere that you'll love coming home to. But wait, there's more! Venture downstairs to discover the finished basement, offering endless possibilities for a cozy entertainment area, home office, or your own private getaway. This home isn't just a house, it's a blank canvas full of potential. It's time to unleash your inner designer and turn this space into the perfect reflection of your unique style and personality.Get ready for the New Year in your NEW HOME!
